Figure-labeled code chunk with overlay:

```{code-cell} python
:type: figure
:label: 1
:caption: A code-generated figure with an annotation overlay.

plot(data)
```

Plain SVG code block in caption should not become overlay:

```{code-cell} python
:type: figure
:label: 2
:caption: ```svg <svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">   <circle cx="5" cy="5" r="4" /> </svg> ```  A figure whose caption includes an SVG example, not an overlay.

plot(other_data)
```
